Minerva Suspends Paraguay Plant After Case of Foot-And-Mouth

-- B y   J e s s i c a   B r i c e
-- 
2011-09-19T21:13:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/minerva-suspends-paraguay-plant-after-case-of-foot-and-mouth.html
Minerva SA said it suspended a
slaughtering plant in  Paraguay  after a case of foot-and-mouth
disease was discovered in the country, according to an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jessica Brice in Sao Paulo at 
